1- DB_SOCKET=/var/run/mysqld/mysqld.sock  in file .env
2- server folder include
    a- npm install express --save
    b- npm install http --save
    c- npm install socket.io --save
    d- npm install nodemon --save-dev
3- establish connection
4- create socket file  include ( constructor & connection & disconnection  )
    call socket file in  server.js